
GENERAL_SECTION
....................................................................
2.0e-4        ! deltime (s)  
100  0.001  ! Max iterations per deltime & frac. tolerance = abs(Xnew - X)/X to reduce iterations (0 = maxiterations)  



OUTPUT_SECTION 
....................................................................
2                 !   units of time for output. 1 = usec 2 = msec 3 = sec.  4 = min.  5 = hr.
1                 ! Species phimole or phimass output: 0=mass fraction; 1=mole fraction; 2=mol/cm^3 
1.0e-9            !  Phi threshold for reporting res/phi
63                ! 63 = D63 for soot D; 0 = volume averaged soot 
0                 !  Time plot output
 
!        Ai-Aj     C1-C2   H1-H2    S1-S2     T1-T2    ! Summed Product specification                    
........................................................................
--------------------------------------------------------------------

 
