........................................................................................
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


SOLVE_SECTION
................................................................................................
0.01          !  Tolerance for sum of species: stop for  Ysum > 1 + tolerance
0.03  1.e-6  ! Default phimag  Minimum phimag
1            ! Intervals of iteration or timestep for Phimag update; 0 = no update from default values.
0.0  0.0     ! Max.Phi DownMovement/Phi; Max.Phi Up Movement/Phimax  0.0 = no restriction   (automatically 0 for unsteady or vode)
1.0          ! Phi URF  (automatically 1 for unsteady or vode)

